::Prowl::

Prowl nods as he recieves Iron Raptor's thought, knowing she was 
probably right. He had been too excited to feel her fear, but that 
wasn't what was getting him down. What was getting him down was that 
she said she no longer trusted him.

-Its ok,- he thinks to her, about to add on to that when Shadow Cat 
arrives. He glances at Iron Raptor, raising an eyebrow.

-An old friend?- he thinks to her, knowing that Shadow Cat couldn't 
hear the thought. This new way of communication between him and Iron 
Raptor could come in very handy...

His scanners pick up Angel Prime heading for his location.

-Arcangel is heading for us,- he thinks to Iron Raptor, -Or someone 
that registers very closely to Arcangel's sign
